---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/lcg.css';
---

<Layout title="About Us - LCG">
  <header>
    <nav>
      <div class="logo-group">
        <a href="/" class="logo">LC<span class="accent">G</span></a>
        <span class="logo-text">
          Lasana Cahaya <span class="accent">G</span>emilang
        </span>
      </div>
      <ul class="nav-menu">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about" class="active">About Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="/insight">Insight</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero" style="min-height: 60vh;">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        <span class="word">About</span>
        <span class="word">Us</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Lasana Cahaya Gemilang: Illuminating pathways to sustainable innovation through bold design and strategic vision.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
      </div>

      <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-3xl); flex-direction: column;">
        <!-- History Tab -->
        <div class="card-feature">
          <h3>History</h3>
          <p>
            Lasana Cahaya Gemilang was founded with a singular vision: to bridge the gap between technological innovation and sustainable impact. What began as a small collective of designers and strategists has evolved into a full-service creative platform serving organizations across water infrastructure, renewable energy, and global logistics.
          </p>
          <p>
            Over the past decade, we've worked with leading institutions to design systems that matter. From water purification networks in Southeast Asia to energy transition frameworks for mid-market enterprises, our work has always centered on one principle: design that serves humanity and the planet.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, LCG stands as a beacon of thoughtful innovation—proof that business and sustainability aren't opposing forces, but natural partners when guided by vision and craft.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Vision & Mission Tab -->
        <div class="card-feature">
          <h3>Vision & Mission</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Our Vision:</strong> A world where sustainable infrastructure is the default, where renewable energy powers human progress, and where global logistics serve communities rather than exploit them.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Our Mission:</strong> To create strategic design solutions that accelerate the transition to sustainable systems. We believe great design is invisible—it solves problems so elegantly that users forget they were ever problems at all.
          </p>
          <p>
            We work at the intersection of three disciplines:
          </p>
          <ul style="max-width: 75ch; margin: var(--space-lg) 0;">
            <li><strong>Strategic Thinking</strong> — Understanding the true needs beneath stated problems</li>
            <li><strong>Design Excellence</strong> — Crafting interfaces and systems with precision and beauty</li>
            <li><strong>Systems Thinking</strong> — Recognizing how each piece affects the whole</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            This is how we create impact that lasts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background-color: var(--color-surface-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <p>The principles that guide every decision.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Radical Honesty</h3>
          <p>We tell you what we think, not what you want to hear. Trust is built on truth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Craft Above All</h3>
          <p>Every detail matters. We obsess over the work because the work matters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Systems Thinking</h3>
          <p>We don't solve problems in isolation. We understand how solutions ripple across systems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Sustainable Impact</h3>
          <p>Short-term wins mean nothing. We design for decades, not quarters.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Let's Work Together</h2>
        <p>Whether you're tackling water infrastructure, transitioning to renewables, or optimizing global supply chains, we're ready to partner.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a Conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h4>About LCG</h4>
        <p>Lasana Cahaya Gemilang is a creative platform dedicated to sustainable innovation and design excellence.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h4>Explore</h4>
        <p><a href="/services">Services</a></p>
        <p><a href="/insight">Insight</a></p>
        <p><a href="/about">About Us</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h4>Connect</h4>
        <p><a href="/contact">Contact</a></p>
        <p><a href="mailto:hello@lcg.creative">hello@lcg.creative</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Lasana Cahaya Gemilang. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  ul {
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
</style>
